          <li>Implement customer retention programs</li>
          <li>Diversify service offerings in recession-resistant areas</li>
          <li>Optimize operational efficiency</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Phase 3 (Days 61-90): Growth Positioning</strong></p>
        <ul>
